<article>
  <p>Hey Flourishites!</p>
  <p>Email notification preferences are out, there should be a link, "Notification Preferences", at the bottom of all emails from now on. Give it a go and let me know if there are any issues.</p>
  <p>There is also a Privacy Statement up, which can be accessed from the footer of each page of Flourish.buzz.</p>
  <p>The next thing on the development board is a, 'Recent Activity', section.</p>
  <p><strong>GitHub:</strong> <%= link_to "A 'Recent Activity' Modal on the Home Page #116", "https://github.com/cassar/flourish/issues/116" %></p>
  <p>I'm always on the lookout for new members, feel free to encourage anyone you think may be interested to checkout the site and join.</p>
  <p>Have a great week!</p>
  <p>-Luke-</p>
</article>
<article>
  <p><b>Distribution <%= @next_distribution.name %> Preview</b></p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Date:</b> <%= @next_distribution.date_formatted %></li>
    <li><b>Total Contributions:</b> <%= @next_distribution.total_pool_formatted(@member.currency) %></li>
    <li><b>Members:</b> <%= @next_distribution.member_count %></li>
    <li><b>Dividend:</b> <%= @next_distribution.dividend_amount_formatted(@member.currency) %></li>
  </ul>
  <a><%= link_to "View Past Distributions", distributions_url %></a>
</article>
<article>
<p><b>Recent Contributions</p></b>
  <% if @recent_contributions.none? %>
    <p>[No contributions in the last week]</p>
  <% else %>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Date</th>
          <th>Amount</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% @recent_contributions.each do |contribution| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= contribution.created_at_formatted %></td>
            <td><%= contribution.amount_formatted %></td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% end %>
</article>
<article>
  <p><b>Weekly Expenses</p></b>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Item</th>
        <th>Amount</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @expenses.each do |expense| %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= expense.name %></td>
          <td><%= expense.amount_formatted %></td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
      <tr>
        <td><b>Total Deducted from Pool</b></td>
        <td><b><%= @total_expenses_formatted %></b></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</article>
